title: Cannot supply primitive array to a @ParameterizedTest

milestone.title: 5.0 M6
milestone.description: Themes: Java 9 compatibility, validation (e.g. tag syntax), and bug fixes

body:
## Overview

Sample code that will produce the error can be found here: https://github.com/braghome/primitive.array
